About--
This dataset contain more than 130k+ cricket news articles from [espncricinfo](http://espncricinfo.com/) scraped using python's scrapy library. It has columns namely:

1. Date of new published
2. headlines
3. summary of news text
4. category of the news article

Explore that dataset and analyze the sentiment of the news.
